#META# contentSummary: A fragmentary list concerning the measurement of different plots of land owned/managed by the *muqaddams* of Warzīkh. The land was measured in *khufch*, which seems to be a vernacular for an unstandardised measurement made by a stick, the length of which may have been locally determined.
